body.description: Furinno Andrey Coffee Table with Bin Drawer is an ideal centerpiece for any living room. Crafted with an emphasis on simplicity and elegance, this functional coffee table showcases a spacious tabletop. It offers ample space to accommodate your favourite books, refreshing beverages, and unique decor items. Adding a touch of timeless charm to your living space, this coffee table seamlessly upgrades and enhances your home, creating a more appealing atmosphere. This exquisite piece of furniture is perfect for your stylish abode. The coffee table is made of CARB-grade composite wood tested for durability and sturdiness, carrying the Programme for the Endorsement of Forest Certification (PEFC). Assembly is easy with provided step-by-step instructions. Care instructions: wipe clean with a clean damped cloth. Avoid using harsh chemicals. Pictures are for illustration purposes. All decor items are not included in this offer. The product is entitled to a 1-year warranty against manufacturer defects.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About the Manufacturer Bridging innovation with simplistic furniture, Furinno brings modern designs to transform your home into a one-of-a-kind oasis that will surely assist the compact and space saving need for your home. Engineered with recycled Malaysian rubberwood, Furinno is committed to making home furnishing easy affordable, and unique while remaining sustainable in the process. Furinno Andrey Living Room Collection Simple and Elegant Design Immerse yourself in a vast array of color and style choices where there are endless possibilities in combination of fashion and elegance with Furinno Andrey Living Room Collection. We provide a wide variety of products that will lighten up and refreshes the look of your living room. Modern color style. Stylish. Functional. Affordable. Easy to assemble.
The Urban Elegance for Modern Living Room Space

Premium Quality Materials Crafted from wood for sturdiness and durability. Lightweight, strong, and long-lasting product usage. Round Edge The wood panels with round edges are designed to avoid potential injuries. Easy Handling Crafted with metal ring for easy handling and adds a touch of elegance to organizational needs. Simplistic Design The simplistic and minimalist design gives the unit flexibility to fit in, no matter the setting of the living room.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for Toddlers!
reviews.reviewText: i got it for my son to use as a coloring table/workbench, it’s perfect toddler height, even if they have a chair. however, the fake wood cover thing? linoleum? idk, it’s peeling off the sides. So it’s perfect for a destructive toddler, but not so much your living room. holds 115lbs on top tho 💀
